sequenceDiagram
  %% Diagram 64: Facebook Shops Sync and Attribution Flow

  autonumber
  actor V as Vendor
  participant API as /api/social/sync/facebook
  participant Sync as Catalog Sync Worker
  participant FB as Facebook Shops API
  participant Store as Mapping Store
  participant Retry as Delta Retry Queue
  participant Analytic as Attribution Engine

  V->>API: Start Facebook catalog sync
  API->>Sync: Enqueue sync job
  Sync->>FB: Push product catalog delta
  FB-->>Sync: Sync response/callback

  alt Token invalid or auth failure
    Sync-->>API: Reconnect required
    API-->>V: Re-authorize Facebook account
  else Sync response received
    alt Partial sync failure
      Sync->>Store: Persist partial status + failed item set
      Sync->>Retry: Enqueue delta retry job
      Retry->>FB: Retry failed catalog delta
      FB-->>Retry: Retry callback
      Retry->>Store: Persist final sync status
      Retry->>Analytic: Emit attribution signal for synced items
      API-->>V: Partial sync recovered summary
    else Full sync success
      Sync->>Store: Persist product mapping + sync status
      Sync->>Analytic: Emit source attribution signal
      Analytic-->>API: Attribution updated
      API-->>V: Sync complete summary
    end
  end
